column1: Desertcreat church 3 miles NE by E
Distances ends in the vicinity of Rockdale House; observer is Lt Col  Lowry who lived in Rockdale House
James Lowry 1835-1897 served in the Royal Artillery, was JP and Deputy Lieutenant for the County
Grid Ref for Rockdale House as on  OS 25" 1888-1913 map
Gauge burst by frost or bottle broken so records below computed from the daily gauge
